      "writtenOn": "2016-08-09T21:09:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Given that this implementation is the same as in the Windows one, it can probably be shared. But I don\u0027t think this operation belongs on the database, as it\u0027s something that a higher-level component can perform.",
